text: A small store where you can get a wide variety of snacks and drinks. Similar to 7 eleven but not so crowded. People running the store are friendly and helpful. Have been patronising this stall whenever I'm in this part of town.
the cash counter lady will promise me you get back your extra paid  amount under 3 working days  today is last day  i wait for amount back  she is give me a slip also
Surprising supermart in the middle of Bencoolen! Had quite a diverse range of goods!
